Description: This listing is for an East Tech Reproduction 6139-60XX Gasket Set. These are Top Quality Reproduction Gaskets from Swiss + Japanese sources. Shown in the last 2 photo's, they have been Pressure Tested to 6ATM's, and Proven Water Tight with no bubbles when submerged. These Gaskets are for the 6139-600X, 6139-601X, and 6139-603X series of Seiko Chronograph watches. This Gasket Set also fits the 6139-6020 + 6139-6022 Pulsations Chronograph but the crystal gasket will not be needed due it having a Tension Ring style crystal. This auction includes the following Reproduction Gaskets: (1) EC3269B crystal gasket, (2) DJ0060B "D" Ring Pusher Gaskets, (1) DJ0160B "D" Ring Crown Gasket, and (1) FH2980B Case Back Gasket. This set will also include (1) extra DJ0060 "D" Ring Crown Gasket to cover the variances between models which use different crown gaskets. The Watch Case + Casing Parts shown in the photos are for display Purposes Only and are NOT INCLUDED
Title: Seiko East Tech 6139-60XX Complete Gasket Set
